# FINAL OBJECTIVE

Transform Catalog Enrichment into the central onboarding pipeline for all new products entering Atlas Health.

Every RFQ, supplier catalog, price list, purchase order, and external product source should pass through this screen before entering the master catalog.

The page should become:

Import → Match → Review → Enrich → Validate → Sync to Zoho

while maintaining the same enterprise UX language already used across Items, Purchasing, Leads, Bills and Dashboard modules.
